                    <img src="~/images/kids.png" alt="Kids" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="width: 100px; height: auto;">
                    <h4 class="card-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ff6347;">Easy Management</h4>
                    <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4682b4;">Easily add, edit, and delete child records and their daily activities.</p>
                    <a href="/Child" class="btn btn-primary" style="border-radius: 20px;">Manage Children</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card" style="border: none; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
