                    <img src="~/images/kids.png" alt="Kids" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="width: 100px; height: auto;">
                    <h4 class="card-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ff6347;">User Friendly</h4>
